<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Choosing your opinion based on which article you like, or who you get to argue with is pretty ignorant if you ask me. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
